<aside class="tools">
    <h2>Helpful tools</h2>
    <p>Here are some of the tools I've used in the past. While I found many of them invaluable and still do, note the ones listed below are in no way prescriptive. Ideally, you should try as many tools as you can find to find out what gets you the best results.</p>
